<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="109" type="dna barcoding">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="109">DNA barcoding.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="109">
BIN BOLD:ADF137. The five specimens sequenced for COI are from two localities on Hawaii and have maximum intraspecific p-distance of 0.17%. The p-distance to the nearest neighbor, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Gracillariidae" genus="Philodoria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Philodoria kauaulaensis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kauaulaensis">Philodoria kauaulaensis</taxonomicName>
